docs/source/design-system.md:1328:2. Company Secretary verifies documents and signs checklist.
docs/source/design-system.md:1333:### 24.4 Behaviour
docs/source/design-system.md:1335:- Display documents grouped by category: KYC, Loan, Security, Bank, Approvals, Closure.
docs/source/design-system.md:1338:- Support upload, preview, replace, mark verified, reject document and add note.
docs/source/design-system.md:1339:- Any replaced document must preserve version history.
docs/source/design-system.md:1340:- A document marked verified must capture verifier, timestamp and method.
docs/source/design-system.md:1341:- Disbursement cannot proceed until mandatory documents are complete.
