docs/source/implementation-roadmap.md:185:| R0 | Discovery Finalisation and Foundation Setup | Team alignment, final decisions, environments, architecture and baseline configuration |
docs/source/implementation-roadmap.md:186:| R1 | Core Platform Foundation | Users, roles, auth, member master, document storage, audit and configuration foundation |
docs/source/implementation-roadmap.md:189:| R4 | Documentation and Security Package | Legal documents, checklist, PoA, SH-4, CDSL, cheques and stamping |
docs/source/implementation-roadmap.md:196:## 6.2 Roadmap Timeline Model
docs/source/implementation-roadmap.md:213:A compressed approach is possible if parallel teams work on backend, frontend, QA, DevOps and document templates simultaneously, but compression should not remove control testing.
