docs/source/implementation-roadmap.md:1915:| Sensitive data exposure | Privacy/legal risk | Encrypt, mask, restrict downloads and audit. |
docs/source/implementation-roadmap.md:1920:| Users resist workflow | Adoption risk | Training, dashboards and mandatory gates. |
