docs/working/REVIEW_FINDINGS.md:404:The `002C` and `002C2` review packets both claim red/green TDD evidence under `evidence/terminal-logs/`, but those directories are not present in the committed run artifacts for `.ralph/runs/2026-07-03_113738_normal_run/` or `.ralph/runs/2026-07-03_115501_normal_run/`. The root gate logs are present and show green backend/frontend validation, but the Ralph workflow requires TDD red/green evidence to be saved before completion. This weakens auditability for high-risk RBAC/auth work even though the final gates passed.
